# Copy to ~/.config/molt/profile.env
# All settings: molt-cli info

# --- Suite picker (no saved default) ---
# clone, pull, check, ssh fix ask every time:
#
#   1) be-*      → ~/Workspace/molt/be/
#   2) web-*     → molt/web/
#   3) mobile-*  → molt/mobile/
#   4) iac-*     → molt/iac/
#   5) all       → runs 1–4 in one command
#
# Skip picker:
#   molt-cli clone --prefix be
#   molt-cli clone --prefix all
#   molt-cli pull --prefix all --rebase
#
# Add a new prefix (e.g. data-*):
#   1. lib/repos-common.sh  → MOLT_VALID_SUITES=(be web mobile iac data)
#   2. lib/prefix.sh        → menu + read choice cases
#   3. mkdir -p ~/Workspace/molt/data
#   4. molt-cli info        → verify workspace_data
# See README.md "Adding a new prefix" for full steps.

# --- GitHub ---
# GITHUB_ORG=molt-digiflux
# MOLT_DEFAULT_BRANCH=env/staging

# --- Git over SSH (default) ---
# MOLT_GIT_PROTOCOL=ssh
# MOLT_GITHUB_HOST=github.com

# --- Identity ---
# GIT_PROMOTE_NAME=Your Name
# GIT_PROMOTE_EMAIL=you@example.com
# MOLT_SCRIPTS_GIT_NAME=Your Name
# MOLT_SCRIPTS_GIT_EMAIL=you@example.com

# --- Workspace ---
# MOLT_ROOT=/home/you/Workspace/molt

# --- Promote ---
# MERGE_STYLE=merge
